Sort a ditto mode file of cities first by country, then by descending population.  But with the row for Toyko pegged.
perltab -test -D -sab,10 'F(city)=~/Toky/? undef : F(coun pop)' t/regression/input/NEAsiaMegacities_ditto.tsv
